headline: Top AI picks from a software engineer turned strategist
summary: Bokeh Capital Partners founder and chief investment officer Kimberly Forrest joins Wealth to explain her strategy for picking stocks in the artificial intelligence (AI) trade and to share two of her top AI stock picks: Micron Technology (MU) and Synopsys (SNPS).
